'''Heptacosylic acid''', or '''heptacosanoic acid''' or '''carboceric acid''', is a 27-[[carbon]] long-chain [[saturated fatty acid]] with the [[chemical formula]] CH<sub>3</sub>(CH<sub>2</sub>)<sub>25</sub>COOH.
